name: Utkarsh Bajaj
blurb: Our founding members saw a huge scope for improvement in the computer science culture at MIT Manipal. Lack of opportunity, information and motivation needed to be eliminated, for MIT to have a thriving culture in the science of computing. To rejuvenate the community, ACM Manipal was set up.
